original_title: The Wiggles Take on The World
overview: Charts the story of the rise of the Wiggles, Anthony Field (Blue Wiggle), Greg Page (Yellow Wiggle), Murray Cook (Red Wiggle), Jeff Fatt (Purple Wiggle) and Paul Field (General Manager) from their beginnings in the band The Cockroaches to their Wiggles superstar / enterprise status taking their successful formula to the children of Asia, the USA and Europe.
title: The Wiggles Take on The World
